{"id":246267,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-山东访民刘厚顺无端被绑架后劳教（图）/","date":"2012-08-09T22:16:11Z","modified":"2012-08-09T22:16:11Z","title":"维权网 | 山东访民刘厚顺无端被绑架后劳教（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员关小令报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日上午</span><span>，本网从山东省文登市天福办事处峰西居委会访民刘厚顺的家属口中得知</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>刘厚顺于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>到吉林省永吉县口泉批发市场进货时，被户籍地文登市公安局跟踪抓捕回当地，直接送进烟台劳教所关押，家属至今没有得到公安机关的通知和手续。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据刘厚顺家属说，刘厚顺在被文登市公安局送进烟台劳教所时，其手机还未收走的一刻间，急忙打出电话告诉家属说，他是正在吉林省永吉县口泉市场进货时，被文登市公安局绑架，已于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>押回，直接送到烟台劳教所了。之后家人再也联系不上刘厚顺本人，至今也没收到文登市公安局或政府对刘厚顺的劳教手续。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本网曾经多次关注过访民刘厚顺的案情，并于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>对刘厚顺再次进京揭露他被地方公安绑架、毒打、关押的受害经历，同时立下遗书，不惜生命，誓与腐败斗争到底的决心。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘厚顺</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>曾是一位商人，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月到河南进货路过北京住店时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>被文登市公安局进京抓访民的治安大队大队长丛培庆和副大队长吴俊虎等人将他从投宿的旅店中抓走，又进行殴打致伤，押送回山东文登市释放，却不给一个说法，无故被公安抓捕，又被打伤，还不给治疗，迫使刘厚顺从此走上维权之路。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因上访控告的对象是手握执法生杀大权的公安机关，平时听信政府法律面前人人平等，执法必严，违法必究等宣传，当刘厚顺要求政府有关部门查处公安机关执法犯法行为时，才看清腐败政府愚弄百姓的本质，由于他不断与腐败较真，就不断受到公安和政府的打压，经历</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>次拘留和劳教报复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民刘厚顺陈述今年中央召开两会时被政府官员和公安绑架经过时说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点钟前后，我在北京南站候车大厅里坐着，（我旁边还有福州和蓬莱访民），突然遭到文登市常驻北京的截访人刘曾林和江华带领一帮警察非法绑架，当时，他们突然上来把我按倒在座位上，强行把我的双手背拷，用文登市公安局专用手提包把我的头套住，我喘不过气来，差点就把我憋死。他们从候车大厅的东边门把我押出来，把我塞进汽车遣返文登，我的上访材料、生活用品和背篼都给我扔掉了，途中调换过一次汽车，在汽车里他们边殴打我边对我进行恐吓，说：我都枪毙过人。次日早晨把我拉到文登，我的双手肿的发亮棉衣都被血液浸透了，我的手腕和双臂不能动弹了，被公安局送进医院治疗十天，他们</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时看守怕我上北京，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>北京两会结束，下午把我送进拘留所，竟然非法关押我长达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>天，而且这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>天都是用手铐把我靠在床上，摧残我的身体都不能大便，公安局把我拉到医院洗肠。我的身体被公安局摧残的留下很多的后遗症至今不好。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>中央“十八大”</span><span> </span><span>会议临近，中央一再强调要切实解决访民问题，而地方政府对那些早已不再相信欺骗的访民，仍然采取绑架、关黑监狱、劳教等方式控制访民，刘厚顺又是一起典型案例，希望引起有关部门的重视。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-La3amylKEuI/UCPTEx-fC3I/AAAAAAAALJs/4-PaiNwr7Yg/s1600/%E6%89%93%E4%BC%A4%E8%BA%BA%E5%9C%A8%E8%BD%A6%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%88%98%E5%8E%9A%E9%A1%BA.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"179\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-La3amylKEuI/UCPTEx-fC3I/AAAAAAAALJs/4-PaiNwr7Yg/s320/%E6%89%93%E4%BC%A4%E8%BA%BA%E5%9C%A8%E8%BD%A6%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%88%98%E5%8E%9A%E9%A1%BA.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>此前被绑架打伤的刘厚顺</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>附：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年对刘厚顺的劳动教养决定书</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>刘厚顺，男，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1954</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>日</span><span>出生，民族：汉族，身份证件号码：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">370632195410310053</span><span>，文化程度：高中，职业：无，工作单位：无，户籍所在地：文登市天福办事处峰西居委会，现住址：文登市永乐街东</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>巷</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>号。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>因扰乱单位秩序被北京公安局朝阳分局行政拘留五日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>因扰乱单位秩序被文登市公安局行政拘留十日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>因故意损坏公私财物被文登市公安局行政拘留七日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>违法犯罪事实和证据：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时</span><span>许，刘厚顺在北京市朝阳区三里屯马河南岸路边处以手举上访材料，含冤的方式进行上访活动，引起路人驻足围观，严重扰乱了该地区公共场所秩序，且不听民警劝阻，被北京市公安局朝阳分局行政拘留五日；以上事实有北京市公安局朝阳分局京公</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[</span><span>朝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span><span>决定</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[2006]</span><span>第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12205</span><span>号公安行政处罚决定书</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>刘厚顺本人陈述予以证实。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>时许，刘厚顺在北京市公安部信访接待处门口上访期间大声吵闹，欲强行进入信访办并动手厮打工作人员，严重扰乱了公安部信访接待处的工作秩序，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>被文登市公安局以文登市公安局文公</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[</span><span>城里分局</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span><span>决定</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[2007]</span><span>第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1139</span><span>号公安行政处罚决定书决定处罚拘留十日；以上事实刘厚顺本人陈述</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>证人董某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>于某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>金某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>吴某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>邵某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>李某证人证言</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>检查笔录予以证实。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分许，刘厚顺在文登市公安局拘留所内执行拘留期间，无理取闹将拘留所内的烟灰缸</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>办公用品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>窗玻璃砸坏，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>被文登市公安局以文登市公安局文公</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[</span><span>张</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span><span>决定</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[2007]</span><span>第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1903</span><span>号公安行政处罚决定书决定行政拘留七日。以上事实有刘厚顺本人、陈述</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>证人阚某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>张某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>原某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>于某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>迟某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>田某</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>丛某证人证言</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>办案情况说明</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>物证照片予以证实。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>综上所述，刘厚顺多次违反治安管理，屡教不改，在其执行拘留期间，无故滋事，任意损毁公私财物，情节恶劣。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>根据</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[[</span><span>国务院关于劳动教养问题的决定</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">]]</span><span>第一条第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[1]</span><span>项</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.[[</span><span>劳动教养试行办法</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">]]</span><span>第十一条</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>第十三条之规定，现决定对刘厚顺劳动教养壹年零个月。劳动教养期限自执行之日起计算，此前关押一日折抵劳动教养期限一日，即自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>如不服本决定，可在接到本决定书之日起的六十日内，向威海市人民政府或山东省劳动教养管理委员会</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[</span><span>地址：济南市经二路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">185</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span><span>申请行政复议，或者在接到本决定书之日起的三个月内直接向人民法院提起行政诉讼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>威海市劳动教养管理委员会</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> 2007<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span></span>10<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>24<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p></div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4090220733261885487?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,17850,20534],"tags":[16910,28519]}